**Running Locally:**  
Running this command \`mvn exec:java\` with this pom.xml configuration:
 \<plugin\>  
                \<groupId\>org.codehaus.mojo\</groupId\>  
                \<artifactId\>exec-maven-plugin\</artifactId\>  
                \<version\>3.1.0\</version\>  
                \<configuration\>  
                    \<mainClass\>hadoop.mapreduce.tp1.WordCount\</mainClass\>  
                    \<arguments\>  
                        \<argument\>src/main/resources/input/file.txt\</argument\>  
                        \<argument\>src/main/resources/output\</argument\>  
                    \</arguments\>  
                \</configuration\>  
            \</plugin\>

and the results are:  
![][image7]

and the content of output.txt is:  
![][image8]
